  "description": "Physical string at maximum stiffness with minimal damping — the string rings like a struck hardwood bar. Excite near the bridge (high excitePos), narrow exciter, fixed boundary. Zero sustain force for pure transient decay. A xylophone-adjacent plucked fundamental.",
